{
  "an8.53:0.1": "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8 ",
  "an8.53:0.2": "6. Gotamīvagga ",
  "an8.53:0.3": "53. Saṅkhittasutta ",
  "an8.53:1.1": "Ekaṁ samayaṁ bhagavā vesāliyaṁ viharati mahāvane kūṭāgārasālāyaṁ. ",
  "an8.53:1.2": "Atha kho mahāpajāpatī gotamī yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṁ abhivādetvā ekamantaṁ aṭṭhāsi. Ekamantaṁ ṭhitā kho sā mahāpajāpatī gotamī bhagavantaṁ etadavoca: ",
  "an8.53:2.1": "“Sādhu me, bhante, bhagavā saṅkhittena dhammaṁ desetu, yamahaṁ bhagavato dhammaṁ sutvā ekā vūpakaṭṭhā appamattā ātāpinī pahitattā vihareyyan”ti. ",
  "an8.53:2.2": "“Ye kho tvaṁ, gotami, dhamme jāneyyāsi: ",
  "an8.53:2.3": "‘ime dhammā sarāgāya saṁvattanti, no virāgāya; ",
  "an8.53:2.4": "saṁyogāya saṁvattanti, no visaṁyogāya; ",
  "an8.53:2.5": "ācayāya saṁvattanti, no apacayāya; ",
  "an8.53:2.6": "mahicchatāya saṁvattanti, no appicchatāya; ",
  "an8.53:2.7": "asantuṭṭhiyā saṁvattanti, no santuṭṭhiyā; ",
  "an8.53:2.8": "saṅgaṇikāya saṁvattanti, no pavivekāya; ",
  "an8.53:2.9": "kosajjāya saṁvattanti, no vīriyārambhāya; ",
  "an8.53:2.10": "dubbharatāya saṁvattanti, no subharatāyā’ti, ",
  "an8.53:2.11": "ekaṁsena, gotami, dhāreyyāsi: ",
  "an8.53:2.12": "‘neso dhammo, neso vinayo, netaṁ satthusāsanan’ti. ",
  "an8.53:3.1": "Ye ca kho tvaṁ, gotami, dhamme jāneyyāsi: ",
  "an8.53:3.2": "‘ime dhammā virāgāya saṁvattanti, no sarāgāya; ",
  "an8.53:3.3": "visaṁyogāya saṁvattanti, no saṁyogāya; ",
  "an8.53:3.4": "apacayāya saṁvattanti, no ācayāya; ",
  "an8.53:3.5": "appicchatāya saṁvattanti, no mahicchatāya; ",
  "an8.53:3.6": "santuṭṭhiyā saṁvattanti, no asantuṭṭhiyā; ",
  "an8.53:3.7": "pavivekāya saṁvattanti, no saṅgaṇikāya; ",
  "an8.53:3.8": "vīriyārambhāya saṁvattanti, no kosajjāya; ",
  "an8.53:3.9": "subharatāya saṁvattanti, no dubbharatāyā’ti, ",
  "an8.53:3.10": "ekaṁsena, gotami, dhāreyyāsi: ",
  "an8.53:3.11": "‘eso dhammo, eso vinayo, etaṁ satthusāsanan’”ti. ",
  "an8.53:3.12": "Tatiyaṁ. "
}